name: Unidentified_contractor_(Galactic_Empire)
content: A male Human contractor specialized in magnetic containment vessels. In 1 BBY, he was aboard the civilian transport vessel Nordieus en route to the DS-1 Orbital Battle Station while it was under construction at the planet Despayre. He tried engaging Commander Atour Riten, who was also on the same flight, in talking about the technical requirements of powering the space station.
